thread.title: Tony Zaccari

author: Tony Zaccari
title: Tony Zaccari
text: I have been using Servcorp for over 2 years. The setup is perfect for doing business. It is quiet and relaxed with all the basic facilities and more, that is required by an office, all close at hand.The staff are friendly, competent, knowledgeable and never short of wanting to lend a hand. The office is clean and decor extremely modern allowing you never hesitate bringing valuable clients to the office. I highly recommend Servcorp.
